{"tid":408284,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"雜談幽冥禁忌、盂蘭節","createTime":"2017-09-21T06:04:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T16:14:28.000Z","uid":89349,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de307a34613ff9ae3b68f77ff8bafe5ca0b5e72c","tid":408284,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:04:09.000Z","msg":"華人對冥界之事多禁忌，常被抹黑成保守、落後；月餅廣告充滿幽冥指涉，公關、報章報導也有意無意指是「見人見智」。<br />\n<br />\n時下就是有那麼多人，鄙視傳統禁忌。<br />\n<br />\n關於死亡，他們不想有禁忌，不想有天譴、審判，或輪迴，只想有RIP（rest in peace）。<br />\n<br />\n你罵一句「俾天收」，就是犯了他們的禁忌，他們新的禁忌，就覺得你「涼薄」。<br />\n<br />\n至於紙紥公仔，拿來「玩膠」，做中秋燈籠，他們認為好好玩。他們稱是「百無禁忌」。<br />\n<br />\n華人對冥界之事多禁忌，就是保守、落後？新派港人不認識幽冥符號，便解說成「百無禁忌」。"},{"pid":"24047fbc5ea2f019c3fb3d144682554cadb50e4f","tid":408284,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:07:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/passiontimes/posts/1583992808330547\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpassiontimes%2Fposts%2F1583992808330547&d=EFgSP%2BxOnlTz%2BsPMS8n1iwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c9b27f53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/passiontimes/posts/1583992808330547</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5912e53811cd96edb193fd4f188c5a007df66c92","tid":408284,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/140803_ca1128bf16dea04fa9529102fa1608a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F140803_ca1128bf16dea04fa9529102fa1608a3.jpg&h=e331bb05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0171897e23bd404a4ab3ee16b40faba76e7bc7f5","tid":408284,"uid":73907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:10:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/140803_ca1128bf16dea04fa9529102fa1608a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F140803_ca1128bf16dea04fa9529102fa1608a3.jpg&h=e331bb05&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7db62f9dec1d36e01ba07e4a44ebc55995cf0b","tid":408284,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:29:33.000Z","msg":"禁忌有何社會意義？<br />\n<br />\n有文化，才需要禁忌。禁忌是區隔，區隔出時節、或者社會分工。華人社會因爲已有社會功能和儀式完善的孟蘭節，我們才需要禁忌，分開時節和日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n鬼門關有開有關，悼念死人有時令，七月就要主動在儀式裡照顧亡魂，重陽清明就要拜祭先人。<br />\n<br />\n其他日子，社會就有人不應無故大規模出現幽冥的意象，令大眾恆常活在死亡氣氛，令平常日子也要肅殺渡過。"},{"pid":"6db0161bc2cb2a042bd96973d69a246735316df9","tid":408284,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:34:40.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4c5dfc62b4a31a84dc0a3a1eabc7dfdd28788dee","tid":408284,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:44:24.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"0cd8d6ed28131bb55db318e7efd7b7e3a822b98e","tid":408284,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:29:16.000Z","msg":"蕭傑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b0a4d7aeaa3f73363ec4393ee3a7c7c24fe2b8","tid":408284,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:14:28.000Z","msg":"好文共賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}